            "title": "屯門海盈花園2房套戶連車位580萬成交  一手業主千禧年購入升值1倍",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<iframe allowtransparency=\"true\" attrmap=\"{data-gtm-yt-inspected-10=true}\" src=\"https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article-audio?postId=15706530&amp;cantoneseUrl=&amp;mandarinUrl=\" style=\"border:none;overflow:hidden;position:relative;margin:0;width: 100%;height: 150px;padding-top: 10px;\"></iframe>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">利嘉閣地產青山公路-滿名山分行促成屯門海盈花園中層B室的二手成交個案，單位實用面積約595方呎，屬2房1套間隔，望海景。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">新買家為區內客，認為單位可飽覽全海景，加上連車位，性價比高，決定洽購。業主原以650萬元放售，議價後以580萬元連車位成交，折合實用面積呎價約9748元。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">原業主於2000年以約287萬元一手買入單位，持貨至今轉手，現帳面獲利約293萬元，物業升值約1倍。</p>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article/15706530-%e5%b1%af%e9%96%80%e6%b5%b7%e7%9b%88%e8%8a%b1%e5%9c%922%e6%88%bf%e5%a5%97%e6%88%b6%e9%80%a3%e8%bb%8a%e4%bd%8d580%e8%90%ac%e6%88%90%e4%ba%a4-%e4%b8%80%e6%89%8b%e6%a5%ad%e4%b8%bb%e5%8d%83%e7%a6%a7",
            "image": "https://image.bastillepost.com/704x369/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/08/20240726_PP_TRANSACTION_BP_FB.png.webp",
            "pub_date": "2026-03-05 14:39:12",
            "source": "bastillepost",
            "kind": 2,
            "language": "zh-HK"
        },
        {
            "title": "凱樂苑極高層1房戶 首置客斥480萬元承接 原業主帳面獲利約212.2萬元離場",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<iframe allowtransparency=\"true\" attrmap=\"{data-gtm-yt-inspected-10=true}\" src=\"https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article-audio?postId=15702515&amp;cantoneseUrl=&amp;mandarinUrl=\" style=\"border:none;overflow:hidden;position:relative;margin:0;width: 100%;height: 150px;padding-top: 10px;\"></iframe>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">香港置業西九龍星匯居分行表示，該行剛促成凱樂苑一宗買賣成交，一個極高層一房戶獲外區首置客以 480萬元 承接，實用呎價約 12533元。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">成交單位為凱樂苑D座極高層，實用面積約383平方呎，屬1房間隔，向西北望開揚景。原業主最初叫價約498萬元放盤，約1個月後吸引外區客洽詢，雙方經議價後以480萬元成交，實用呎價約12533元。據悉，新買家為首置客。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">資料顯示，原業主於2019年9月以約267.8萬元購入上述單位，是次易手，帳面獲利約212.2萬元離場。</p>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article/15702515-%e5%87%b1%e6%a8%82%e8%8b%91%e6%a5%b5%e9%ab%98%e5%b1%a41%e6%88%bf%e6%88%b6-%e9%a6%96%e7%bd%ae%e5%ae%a2%e6%96%a5480%e8%90%ac%e5%85%83%e6%89%bf%e6%8e%a5-%e5%8e%9f%e6%a5%ad%e4%b8%bb%e5%b8%b3%e9%9d%a2",
            "image": "https://image.bastillepost.com/704x369/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/08/20240726_PP_TRANSACTION_BP_FB.png.webp",
            "pub_date": "2026-03-05 14:39:13",
            "source": "bastillepost",
            "kind": 2,
            "language": "zh-HK"
        },
        {
            "title": "2026胡潤全球富豪榜出爐 馬斯克再登榜首 張一鳴嬋聯中國首富",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">2026年胡潤全球富豪榜剛出爐，馬斯克再成榜首，中國首富由字節跳動的張一鳴嬋聯。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"字節跳動創辦人張一鳴成為中國首富。AP圖片\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/04/20250403_zhang-yiming_source-ap.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"字節跳動創辦人張一鳴成為中國首富。AP圖片\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/04/20250403_zhang-yiming_source-ap.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">字節跳動創辦人張一鳴成為中國首富。AP圖片</p>\n</a>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">榜單顯示，現年43歲的張一鳴，財富在全球排名第25位，估計其身家達5500億元(人民幣‧下同)；農夫山泉(09633)的鍾晱晱以5150億元身家，排在全球第26位，中國則居次席。</p>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">騰訊(00700)的馬化騰在被估算的財富也達4650億元，全球排第27倍，中國排第3位。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">全球首富馬斯克估計的財富達5.54萬億元，其身家估計在過去1年提升了89%。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/../blogger/2025/09/20250911_blog_l1.jpg.webp\">\n<img src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/../blogger/2025/09/20250911_blog_l1.jpg.webp\"/>\n</a>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">英偉達的黃仁勳也上胡潤全球10大富豪榜，估計財富1.2萬億元，在過去1年增加34%，在全球排第9位。</p>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article/15709693-2026%e8%83%a1%e6%bd%a4%e5%85%a8%e7%90%83%e5%af%8c%e8%b1%aa%e6%a6%9c%e5%87%ba%e7%88%90-%e9%a6%ac%e6%96%af%e5%85%8b%e5%86%8d%e7%99%bb%e6%a6%9c%e9%a6%96-%e5%bc%b5%e4%b8%80%e9%b3%b4%e5%ac%8b%e8%81%af",
            "image": "https://image.bastillepost.com/704x369/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2026/03/20260305.jpg.webp",
            "pub_date": "2026-03-05 14:39:10",
            "source": "bastillepost",
            "kind": 2,
            "language": "zh-HK"
        },
        {
            "title": "港股午後中段曾倒跌 阿里巴巴跌幅擴至逾3%",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">港股午後中段升幅再度明顯收窄，於下午約2時10分曾倒跌，恒生指數稍早前最低見25236點，跌12點。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">截至下午約2時14分，恒指重新轉升，報25277點，升28點；恒生科技指數暫跌約1.05%，報4779點。阿里巴巴(09988)跌逾3%，比亞迪(01211)跌3.9%。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">滙控(00005)升幅收窄至不足2%；友邦(01299)升逾4%，暫是表現最佳藍籌。</p>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article/15709633-%e6%b8%af%e8%82%a1%e5%8d%88%e5%be%8c%e4%b8%ad%e6%ae%b5%e6%9b%be%e5%80%92%e8%b7%8c-%e9%98%bf%e9%87%8c%e5%b7%b4%e5%b7%b4%e8%b7%8c%e5%b9%85%e6%93%b4%e8%87%b3%e9%80%be3",
            "image": "https://image.bastillepost.com/704x369/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/04/HKSTOCK-6.jpg.webp",
            "pub_date": "2026-03-05 14:19:17",
            "source": "bastillepost",
            "kind": 2,
            "language": "zh-HK"
        },
        {
            "title": "台股收復昨天部份失地 收市回升844點或2.57%",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">台股反彈，收復昨天急挫的部份失地；台灣加權指數收報33672點，反彈844點或2.57%。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2023/08/20230704_FI_source-licensed_台股-5-1.jpg.webp\">\n<img src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2023/08/20230704_FI_source-licensed_台股-5-1.jpg.webp\"/>\n</a>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">指數今早最高曾見34319點，當時升幅達1490點。計入今天反彈的844點後，台股本周累計暫仍跌1741點或4.92%。</p>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article/15709572-%e5%8f%b0%e8%82%a1%e6%94%b6%e5%be%a9%e6%98%a8%e5%a4%a9%e9%83%a8%e4%bb%bd%e5%a4%b1%e5%9c%b0-%e6%94%b6%e5%b8%82%e5%9b%9e%e5%8d%87844%e9%bb%9e%e6%88%962-57",
            "image": "https://image.bastillepost.com/704x369/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/04/20230810_FI_source-web_TaiwanStock2-704.jpg.webp",
            "pub_date": "2026-03-05 13:54:52",
            "source": "bastillepost",
            "kind": 2,
            "language": "zh-HK"
        },
        {
            "title": "海港企業去年基礎虧損2200萬元 不派末期息",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">九龍倉置業(01997)旗下的海港企業(00051)公布，2025年度無論是列賬或撇除物業重估的基礎層面，均出現虧損，不擬派末期息。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"海港企業官網\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2026/03/00051-Web.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"海港企業官網\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2026/03/00051-Web.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">海港企業官網</p>\n</a>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">該公司去年列賬虧損2.34億元，較2024年度的虧損約7000萬元擴大2.34倍；不計投資物業重估減值也有基礎虧損2200萬元，對上年度則錄得基礎盈利8300萬元。</p>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">海港企業旗下兩間在港的酒店，去年入住率均按年提升，增幅超越直接競爭對手，客房收入實現雙位數增長，抵銷了市場整體餐飲及宴會業務疲弱的影響，進而帶動酒店恢復錄得營業盈利。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">不過，香港投資物業受到本港零售市場復甦不平衡所影響，收入和營業盈利雙雙下跌 12%。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">內地業務方面，蘇州尼依格羅酒店的入住率和平均房價皆走軟。發展物業已簽約銷售額放緩至4500萬元人民幣，去年底時未售存貨賬面值已按市況撇減，導致計提2.55億元減值撥備。</p>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article/15709263-%e6%b5%b7%e6%b8%af%e4%bc%81%e6%a5%ad%e5%8e%bb%e5%b9%b4%e5%9f%ba%e7%a4%8e%e8%99%a7%e6%90%8d2200%e8%90%ac%e5%85%83-%e4%b8%8d%e6%b4%be%e6%9c%ab%e6%9c%9f%e6%81%af",
            "image": "https://image.bastillepost.com/704x369/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/03/00051_web_fb.jpg.webp",
            "pub_date": "2026-03-05 12:34:50",
            "source": "bastillepost",
            "kind": 2,
            "language": "zh-HK"
        },
        {
            "title": "半日收市︱升後整固 恒指升212點報25462點 金融股成反彈功臣",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">港股經歷3日受中東戰事影響被拖低的跌市後，今早跟隨外圍反彈並反覆整固，以滙控(00005)為首的重磅金融股是撐市主力。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"圖片來源：滙控官網\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/03/20250305_FI_source-web_HSBC-8.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"圖片來源：滙控官網\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/03/20250305_FI_source-web_HSBC-8.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">圖片來源：滙控官網</p>\n</a>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">恒生指數今早高開334點後全程維持升市，最高曾見25736點，將升幅擴大至487點或1.93%，補回昨天下挫的裂口後隨即回順，於中午臨收市前出現的半日低位25451點時仍升201點；恒指中午收報25462點，升212點或0.84%。</p>\n<!-- slider begin -->\n<div class=\"fancy-slider\">\n<p class=\"fancy-gallery-tips\" style=\"font-weight: bold;font-size: 18px; margin: 0\">點擊看圖輯</p>\n<div class=\"fancy-main\">\n<div class=\"swiper-wrapper\">\n<div class=\"swiper-slide\">\n<a class=\"fancy-main__slide\" data-caption=\"圖片來源：滙控官網\" data-fancybox=\"slider-gallery\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/03/20250305_FI_source-web_HSBC-8.jpg.webp\">\n<div class=\"fancy-main__image\">\n<img alt=\"圖片來源：滙控官網\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/03/20250305_FI_source-web_HSBC-8.jpg.webp\"/>\n</div>\n<h3 class=\"h3 fancy-main__title bpcategory-special-color\">圖片來源：滙控官網</h3>\n</a>\n</div>\n<div class=\"swiper-slide\">\n<a class=\"fancy-main__slide\" data-caption=\"AP圖片\" data-fancybox=\"slider-gallery\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/04/20230808_FI_source-ap_港股12.jpg.webp\">\n<div class=\"fancy-main__image\">\n<img alt=\"AP圖片\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/04/20230808_FI_source-ap_港股12.jpg.webp\"/>\n</div>\n<h3 class=\"h3 fancy-main__title bpcategory-special-color\">AP圖片</h3>\n</a>\n</div>\n<div class=\"swiper-slide\">\n<a class=\"fancy-main__slide\" data-caption=\"圖片來源：友邦保險官網\" data-fancybox=\"slider-gallery\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/04/bplib_20230703-171650__source-web_01299.jpg.webp\">\n<div class=\"fancy-main__image\">\n<img alt=\"圖片來源：友邦保險官網\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/04/bplib_20230703-171650__source-web_01299.jpg.webp\"/>\n</div>\n<h3 class=\"h3 fancy-main__title bpcategory-special-color\">圖片來源：友邦保險官網</h3>\n</a>\n</div>\n<div class=\"swiper-slide\">\n<a class=\"fancy-main__slide\" data-caption=\"圖片來源：九龍倉置業官網\" data-fancybox=\"slider-gallery\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/05/20240507_FI_source-web_01997-Harbour-City-3.jpg.webp\">\n<div class=\"fancy-main__image\">\n<img alt=\"圖片來源：九龍倉置業官網\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/05/20240507_FI_source-web_01997-Harbour-City-3.jpg.webp\"/>\n</div>\n<h3 class=\"h3 fancy-main__title bpcategory-special-color\">圖片來源：九龍倉置業官網</h3>\n</a>\n</div>\n<div class=\"swiper-slide\">\n<a class=\"fancy-main__slide\" data-caption=\"AP圖片\" data-fancybox=\"slider-gallery\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/05/20250526_FI_source-ap_09988.jpg.webp\">\n<div class=\"fancy-main__image\">\n<img alt=\"AP圖片\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/05/20250526_FI_source-ap_09988.jpg.webp\"/>\n</div>\n<h3 class=\"h3 fancy-main__title bpcategory-special-color\">AP圖片</h3>\n</a>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"fancy-main__controls\">\n<div class=\"fancy-main__controls-text bpcategory-special-color\">更多相片</div>\n<div class=\"fancy-main__buttons\">\n<div class=\"fancy-main__button __prev fancy-main-prev\" style=\"border-right: 8px solid #996600\"></div>\n<div class=\"rule\"></div>\n<div class=\"fancy-main__button __next fancy-main-next\" style=\"border-left: 8px solid #996600\"></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"fancy-thumbs\">\n<div class=\"swiper-wrapper\">\n<div class=\"swiper-slide\">\n<div class=\"fancy-thumbs__image\">\n<img alt=\"圖片來源：滙控官網\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/03/20250305_FI_source-web_HSBC-8.jpg.webp\"/>\n</div>\n<h3 class=\"h3 fancy-thumbs__title bpcategory-special-color\">圖片來源：滙控官網</h3>\n</div>\n<div class=\"swiper-slide\">\n<div class=\"fancy-thumbs__image\">\n<img alt=\"AP圖片\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/04/20230808_FI_source-ap_港股12.jpg.webp\"/>\n</div>\n<h3 class=\"h3 fancy-thumbs__title bpcategory-special-color\">AP圖片</h3>\n</div>\n<div class=\"swiper-slide\">\n<div class=\"fancy-thumbs__image\">\n<img alt=\"圖片來源：友邦保險官網\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/04/bplib_20230703-171650__source-web_01299.jpg.webp\"/>\n</div>\n<h3 class=\"h3 fancy-thumbs__title bpcategory-special-color\">圖片來源：友邦保險官網</h3>\n</div>\n<div class=\"swiper-slide\">\n<div class=\"fancy-thumbs__image\">\n<img alt=\"圖片來源：九龍倉置業官網\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/05/20240507_FI_source-web_01997-Harbour-City-3.jpg.webp\"/>\n</div>\n<h3 class=\"h3 fancy-thumbs__title bpcategory-special-color\">圖片來源：九龍倉置業官網</h3>\n</div>\n<div class=\"swiper-slide\">\n<div class=\"fancy-thumbs__image\">\n<img alt=\"AP圖片\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/05/20250526_FI_source-ap_09988.jpg.webp\"/>\n</div>\n<h3 class=\"h3 fancy-thumbs__title bpcategory-special-color\">AP圖片</h3>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<!-- slider end -->\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">恒生科技指數明顯跑輸，半日僅升不足1點或0.01%，報4829點；國企指數升20點或0.24%，報8504點。主板半日成交1641.85億元。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">即月期指半日升245點，報25377點，低水85點。科指期貨升6點，報4824點，低水6點。國指期貨升23點，報8496點，低水8點。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"AP圖片\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/04/20230808_FI_source-ap_港股12.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"AP圖片\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/04/20230808_FI_source-ap_港股12.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">AP圖片</p>\n</a>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">金融股是撐市的大功臣，滙控成功躋身藍籌升幅10大榜上，半日回升3.14%，報134.9元，單一股份已為恒指提供逾77點進賬；另一國際金融股友邦(01299)更是表現次佳藍籌，漲3.95%，報84.2元，亦對恒指帶來超過54點升幅。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">事實上，恒生金融分類指數的10隻成分股今早幾乎全線報升，友邦與滙控升幅位居前列，中銀香港(02388)、港交所(00388)、招商銀行(03968)也升超過1%。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"圖片來源：友邦保險官網\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/04/bplib_20230703-171650__source-web_01299.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"圖片來源：友邦保險官網\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/04/bplib_20230703-171650__source-web_01299.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">圖片來源：友邦保險官網</p>\n</a>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">生科藥業板塊與本地地產股今早亦跑贏大市，中國生物製藥(01177)穩坐藍籌升幅榜首，升5.95%，報6.05元；翰森製藥(03692)在藍籌升幅榜排第4位，升3.5%，報33.12元；信達生物(01801)也升3.22%，報80.1元。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">藍籌本地地產股多半跑贏大市，九龍倉置業(01997)升3.58%，報27.76元；恒隆地產(00101)升2.78%，報9.62元；領展(00823)亦漲2.24%，報38.32元；新鴻基地產(00016)升2.01%，報142.3元；恒基地產(00012)與升1.31%，報34.04元。</p>\n\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"圖片來源：九龍倉置業官網\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/05/20240507_FI_source-web_01997-Harbour-City-3.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"圖片來源：九龍倉置業官網\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/05/20240507_FI_source-web_01997-Harbour-City-3.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">圖片來源：九龍倉置業官網</p>\n</a>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">重磅科股則互有升跌，或多或少限制了大市升勢。今早拖大市後腿的科股主要是阿里巴巴(09988)，集團旗下千問團隊出現人事變動，摩根大通隨即發報告評論，雖然維持對該股「增持」評級，目標價210元，但亦相信千問人事變動事件或引發短期風險溢價。</p>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">阿里巴巴今早大部份時間逆市報跌，中午收報128.4元，跌1.16%。在其他重磅科股中，美團(03690)與網易(09999)均高開低走；昨天遭標準普爾降信用評級的美團，今早跌1.72%，報74.1元；網易也跌1.87%，報178.3元。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"AP圖片\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/05/20250526_FI_source-ap_09988.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"AP圖片\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/05/20250526_FI_source-ap_09988.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">AP圖片</p>\n</a>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">相反，近期亦顯弱勢的小米(01810)，今早則成功反彈1.56%，報32.5元；騰訊(00700)也全程報升，中午收報508.5元，升0.49%。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">京東系將於今日收市後派成績表，各公司早市股價個別發展。龍頭股京東(09618)高開低收，倒跌0.71%，報97.3元；京東物流(02618)跌1.05%，報10.34元；京東健康(06618)早市大部份時間報跌，中午收報49.48元，跌2.31%，是表現最差藍籌；系內半新股京東工業(07618)則突圍而出，升4.02%，報11.12元。</p>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">另外，重型機電設備股持續炒作，東方電氣(01072)與上海電氣(02727)的A股早市初段已漲停板，H股在港明顯受捧。東方電氣升14.26%，報43.44元；上海電氣也升14.82%，報4.88元。</p>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article/15709233-%e5%8d%8a%e6%97%a5%e6%94%b6%e5%b8%82%ef%b8%b1%e5%8d%87%e5%be%8c%e6%95%b4%e5%9b%ba-%e6%81%92%e6%8c%87%e5%8d%87212%e9%bb%9e%e5%a0%b125462%e9%bb%9e-%e9%87%91%e8%9e%8d%e8%82%a1%e6%88%90%e5%8f%8d%e5%bd%88",
