            "title": "A股半日揚升   人大開幕利好",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">A股大幅反彈，深股升逾1%，兩市成交合計15478.37億元(人民幣‧下同)。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">人大會議今早開幕，疊加外圍股市反彈，內地股市回升。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"AP圖片\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/04/20240307_FI_source-ap_AShare-16.png.webp\">\n<img alt=\"AP圖片\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/04/20240307_FI_source-ap_AShare-16.png.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">AP圖片</p>\n</a>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">上證綜指半日升34點或0.84%，報4116點，今早以4109點開市，升27點或0.67%，最低見4090，升8點或0.2%，兩會宣讀工作報告期間升幅擴大，最高見4123點，升41點或1%，半日成交6822.15億元。</p>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">深證成指半日升232點或1.67%，報14150點，今早開市已重越14000點，開報14160點，升242點或1.74%，最低報14059，升142點或1.02%，中段見14202，升285點或2.05%，為半日高位，半日成交8656.22億元。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">滬深300指數半日升60點或1.31%，報4662，今早開升49點或1.07%，開報4651點；</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">創業板指數半日報3241，升76點或2.43%，今早開市報3236點，升71點或2.27%。</p>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article/15708827-a%e8%82%a1%e5%8d%8a%e6%97%a5%e6%8f%9a%e5%8d%87-%e4%ba%ba%e5%a4%a7%e9%96%8b%e5%b9%95%e5%88%a9%e5%a5%bd",
